      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Washington Water Power\ncompany has a large crew Of men\nat work erecting the poles for its\nnew extension of the Lidgerwood\ncar line from Liberty avenue north\nq mile and three-quarters to Rowan\navenue. The work on the new ex-\ntension on Division street. between\nthe same points, is being carried\nalong with the Addison street line.\n\n\nThis will be busy week for the\ncity council. Tomorrow night there\nwill be the regular semi-monthly\nsession, an adjourned session on\nWednesday night and a special\nmeeting Thursday night to con-\nslider the North Coast and Mil\nwaukee franchises."
    }
  ]
